fulltitle: US Congress: Human Rights in Guatemala and Honduras
title: US Congress: Human Rights in Guatemala and Honduras
_filename: _US Congress - Human Rights in Guatemala and Honduras.webm
description: MAY 11, 1998 | Subcommittee members heard testimony on human rights violations and outrages in Guatemala and Honduras. Members of human rights organizations urged the release of classified documents relating to these crimes.
